usecase.event

Interface EventManage

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EventManager

    public interface EventManage
extends java.io.Serializable
    EventManage contains all Event for a conference. EventManage uses Schedule to ensure no double booking of time and location.
    See Also:
    Schedule
